    "Finally, yet important, this paper is meant to underline the main core of GenAI: data.",
    "Once again, a new technology is developed and gravitates around data, opening a new door for regulating usage and control of data, while providing the opportunity to enforce the already existing regulations in a new field, for new sets of data.",
